# re.Term Client — Environment Variables
#
# In dev: WS URL is auto-detected from window.location.hostname
#   → localhost:5173  uses  ws://localhost:3003
#   → 100.77.70.7:5173  uses  ws://100.77.70.7:3003  (Tailscale — auto)
#
# Override only if you need a fixed URL (e.g. production domain):
# VITE_WS_URL=wss://your-domain.com
